title: Dhaba Beas - Sokolovska
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Buffet, Fast food, Salad bar, European
description: Well-known chain of Indian vegetarian dhaba buffets (self service) with a casual, modern atmosphere. Offers both Indian and European vegetarian food including salads and freshly made juices. Food is priced by weight. Happy hour discount 50% off one hour before closing time.
